{"tid":2495818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"耶和華沒有為祂的選民再建一個新以色列。民族是靈魂，土地是肉體","createTime":"2021-04-19T11:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T12:58:00.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3245ab81c0ce8404afad5cbfb4be118a2c7d9d","tid":2495818,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WingCheungHK/posts/10217551280287691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWingCheungHK%2Fposts%2F10217551280287691&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx2iIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=35fec632\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WingCheungHK/posts/10217551280287691</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：周竪峰<br />\n<br />\n猶太人離散千年，最終復國之時，還是得要回到迦南地以色列復國。耶和華並沒有為祂的選民再建一個新以色列。<br />\n<br />\n如果民族是靈魂，土地就是肉體。沒有了靈魂的肉體自是空殼死屍，但沒有了肉體的靈魂也只能是游魂野鬼。靈魂可以不滅，但終歸還是要回到那本初的容器。<br />\n<br />\n香港是它的人，但也是它的土地。"},{"pid":"f2925bbd90ba7410ba20609e832b14d80289f282","tid":2495818,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"哭牆= 天星5 支旗桿<br />\n聖殿山 = 太平山<br />\n各各他 = 荔枝角收押所"}]}